OL,3,CMan wrongfully jailed for murder sees
OL,4,Ccompensation cut to cover 'jail
OL,5,Cexpenses'
OL,7,FNow Mr O'Brien says he is considering
OL,8,Fsuing the UK Government, who have so
OL,9,Ffar refused to reimburse the money.
OL,11,F"11 years and 43 days I was in prison,
OL,12,Fthrough no fault of my own - so why
OL,13,Fshould I pay this board?" he told ITV
OL,14,FCymru Wales.
OL,16,F"I'm just hoping the pubic will get
OL,17,Fbehind us because we need to change
OL,18,Fthis law."
