OL,3,CMan wrongfully jailed for murder sees
OL,4,Ccompensation cut to cover 'jail
OL,5,Cexpenses'
OL,7,FMr O'Brien's nightmare started in
OL,8,F1987, when he and two other men -
OL,9,FDarren Hall and Ellis Sherwood - were
OL,10,Farrested over the brutal murder of
OL,11,FCardiff newsagent Phillip Saunders.
OL,13,FMr Saunders had been attacked on his
OL,14,Fway home from work, in an attempt -
OL,15,Fpolice said - to rob him of his #500
OL,16,Fin takings.
OL,18,FThe 52-year-old had been violently
OL,19,Fbeaten around the head, with a blood-
OL,20,Fspattered spade being found near his
OL,21,Fbody.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/13
