OL,7,F"It's had a profound effect on me," he
OL,8,Fsaid.
OL,10,F"l lost my daughter when I was on
OL,11,Fremand, she died of cot death. My
OL,12,Fstepfather died when I was in prison.
OL,13,FIt destroyed my marriage.
OL,15,F"I haven't spoken to my son for nearly
OL,16,F12 years. And I do find it really
OL,17,Fdifficult.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G6/13
