OL,7,F"I suffer from post-traumatic stress
OL,8,Fdisorder, still. I'm on medication.
OL,9,FI'm still seeing a psychiatrist and
OL,10,FI'm probably going to do that for the
OL,11,Frest of my life."
OL,13,FLast year, the UK Government announced
OL,14,Fthat financial awards made as part of
OL,15,Fthe Miscarriage of Justice scheme
OL,16,Fwould no longer have saved living
OL,17,Fexpenses deducted.
