OL,7,FIt came following the release of
OL,8,FAndrew Malkinson from Greater
OL,9,FManchester, who served 17 years
OL,10,Ffollowing a wrongful conviction for
OL,11,Frape.
OL,13,FBut, crucially, the Ministry of
OL,14,FJustice says the changes won't apply
OL,15,F"retrospectively".
OL,17,F"Financial awards made after 6 August
OL,18,F2023 as part of the Miscarriage of
OL,19,FJustice scheme will not have saved
OL,20,Fliving expenses deducted," a
OL,21,Fspokesperson said.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G8/13
