OL,7,F"However, in line with the standard
OL,8,Fapproach to changes in government
OL,9,Fpolicy, the change announced last year
OL,10,Fdoes not apply retrospectively."
OL,12,FMatt Foot, a co-director with legal
OL,13,Fcharity Appeal, says the change should
OL,14,Fapply to historical cases like Mr
OL,15,FO'Brien's.
OL,17,F"The reason (the UK Government) have
OL,18,Fchanged this law is because everybody
OL,19,Faccepts that this is wrong," he said.
