OL,7,F"So once we've accepted this, it
OL,8,Fnaturally follows that anyone who's
OL,9,Fbeen subject to it should have that
OL,10,Fmoney recouped."
OL,12,FMr Foot believes there's a good chance
OL,13,Fof success for any legal action.
OL,15,F"I think there is a very good
OL,16,Fprospect, both politically and
OL,17,Flegally, that they can recoup this
OL,18,Fmoney because we're talking about
OL,19,Fsmall numbers of people who've been
OL,20,Fsubject to this," he added.
