OL,7,FPaul Blackburn, who served 20 years
OL,8,Fafter a wrongful conviction for
OL,9,Fattempted murder, is also campaigning
OL,10,Fto have saved living costs refunded.
OL,12,FAs is John Kamara, whose murder
OL,13,Fconviction was ruled unsafe in 2001,
OL,14,Ftwo decades after he was sent to
OL,15,Fprison.
OL,17,FMr O'Brien says there are others who
OL,18,Fhave been affected, but that the
OL,19,Famount of money at stake for the
OL,20,Fgovernment is not that large.
