OL,4,Ccompensation cut to cover 'jail
OL,5,Cexpenses'
OL,7,F"The figures we're looking at are not
OL,8,Fthat big," he said.
OL,10,F"When you consider the cost of being
OL,11,Fin prison in the first place and then
OL,12,Foffset that by paying us what they owe
OL,13,Fus, it's only a fraction of the cost
OL,14,Fof keeping someone in prison for one
OL,15,Fyear.
OL,17,F"So it just makes no sense."
OL,19,FMichael O'Brien has started an online
OL,20,Fpetition which has attracted 50,000
OL,21,Fsignatures so far.
